Clare David Moore escaped from a North Carolina prison three times in the 1970s . 
  Moore has been living in Kentucky since at least 2009 . 
  His health is poor from a stroke late last year and he has difficulty speaking . 
  He called police this week to surrender . 
  Moore was convicted of larceny of more than $200 in 1967 and was sentenced to prison . 
  He escaped from prison in 1971 and was recaptured in 1975 . 
  His third escape was in 1976 . 
 